OL,3,C'No doubt' UK will spend 3% of GDP on
OL,4,Cdefence by mid-2030s, Healey says
OL,6,FThe defence secretary has promised a
OL,7,F'certain decade of rising defence
OL,8,Fspending', as ITV News Reporter
OL,9,FVincent McAviney explains
OL,11,FDefence spending at 3% of GDP by 2034
OL,12,Fis a firm commitment, John Healey has
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FThe Government has previously set out
OL,16,Fits "ambition to reach 3% in the next
OL,17,Fparliament", after meeting its pledge
OL,18,Fto ratchet up defence spending to 2.5%
OL,19,Fof GDP by April 2027.
