OL,3,C'No doubt' UK will spend 3% of GDP on
OL,4,Cdefence by mid-2030s, Healey says
OL,6,FBut the Defence Secretary has promised
OL,7,Fa "certain decade of rising defence
OL,8,Fspending", according to The Times, and
OL,9,Fsaid there was "no doubt" the UK would
OL,10,Fmeet its target.
OL,12,FMr Healey told the newspaper: "It
OL,13,Fallows us to plan for the long term.
OL,14,FIt allows us to deal with the
OL,15,Fpressures."
OL,17,FThe Government is looking at the
OL,18,Froles, capabilities and reforms
OL,19,Frequired by UK armed forces as part of
OL,20,Fits strategic defence review (SDR).
