OL,3,C'No doubt' UK will spend 3% of GDP on
OL,4,Cdefence by mid-2030s, Healey says
OL,6,FThe new defence money will be found by
OL,7,Freducing UK overseas aid from 0.5% to
OL,8,F0.3% of GNI (gross national income),
OL,9,Faccording to the Government, a move
OL,10,Fwhich prompted then-international
OL,11,Fdevelopment minister Anneliese Dodds
OL,12,Fto resign.
OL,14,F"You have maintained that you want to
OL,15,Fcontinue support for Gaza, Sudan and
OL,16,FUkraine; for vaccination; for climate;
OL,17,Fand for rules-based systems," she told
OL,18,FSir Keir.
